{#
name: Data Sync
description: Sync data between source and destination with configurable mode and schedule
tags: [integration, sync, data, etl]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of data sync purpose
    required: true
  - name: source
    type: str
    description: Source system or data location (e.g. db:postgres, api:salesforce)
    required: true
  - name: destination
    type: str
    description: Destination system or data location (e.g. db:warehouse, s3:bucket)
    required: true
  - name: sync_mode
    type: str
    description: Sync mode (e.g. full, incremental, append)
    default: "incremental"
  - name: schedule
    type: str
    description: Cron expression or interval (e.g. "0 */6 * * *" for every 6h)
    default: "0 * * * *"
examples:
  - "Sync orders from Postgres to warehouse daily"
  - "Incremental sync from API to S3 every 6 hours"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: integration
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 同步配置

- 源：{{ source }}
- 目标：{{ destination }}
- 模式：{{ sync_mode }}
- 调度：{{ schedule }}

## 同步逻辑

1. 按 schedule 触发任务
2. 从 source 拉取数据
3. 按 sync_mode 处理（全量/增量/追加）
4. 写入 destination
5. 记录同步状态与进度

## 注意事项

- sync_mode 为 incremental 时需有增量键
- schedule 为 cron 表达式，默认每小时
- 建议对大批量数据做分页或流式处理
